{"root":{"data":{"id":"di2c7je3vao0","created":1777130565863,"text":"游戏概念与机制设想","expandState":"expand","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2ck8uj1ow0","created":1777131561646,"text":"世界观与背景概念","layout":null,"expandState":"expand","color":"#000000","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2cs8ve1s80","created":1777132188611,"text":"思维细节\"一瞥\"","layout":null,"background":"#c0504d","color":"#000000","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2csh789r40","created":1777132206741,"text":"是巨大悬浮碎石的天空，鲸鱼在云间游过？慢迁徙？","layout":null,"background":"transparent","color":"#d9d9d9","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di2cswppvpc0","created":1777132240511,"text":"是废弃空间站里，生锈仪表盘上最后一抹闪烁的微光？","background":"transparent","layout":null,"color":"#d9d9d9","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di2ct8g8p0o0","created":1777132266060,"text":"是雨水倒流的城市，人们撑着伞向天空行走？","background":"transparent","layout":null,"color":"#d9d9d9","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di2ctejzqk80","created":1777132279347,"text":"还是一只机械甲虫，驮着整座村庄在沙漠上缓慢迁徙？","background":"transparent","layout":null,"color":"#d9d9d9","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"di2cf6favig0","created":1777131164551,"text":"角色艺术概念","layout_mind_offset":{"x":709.999971787136,"y":159.99999364217143},"layout":null,"expandState":"expand","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2cfcoclq00","created":1777131178159,"text":"玩家在非战斗状态是一个可爱角色形象, 但在战斗状态切换为一个酷的风格, 但整体保持美术风格统一, 类似于埼玉的那种反差感","layout":null,"expandState":"expand","background":"transparent","color":"#d9d9d9","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di3668jm1ig0","created":1777215097185,"text":"角色名: Nina\n性别:女","expandState":"expand","background":"#e36c0a","color":"#d9d9d9","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31ckk3e480","created":1777201487971,"text":"我角色有没有可能是一个人形态树?","background":"#d99594","layout":null,"color":"#000000","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31d6hkmww0","created":1777201535707,"text":"攀爬和地面行走都可以是藤曼或者树根在地理前行(潜行)","layout":null,"color":"#d9d9d9","background":"transparent","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"di2chepwpq80","created":1777131339335,"text":"角色能力","expandState":"expand","layout":null,"font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2c834w6bk0","created":1777130608842,"text":"连招系统","layout":null,"expandState":"expand","background":"#e36c0a","color":"#000000","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2c8i7cdi80","created":1777130641642,"text":"将连击的每段设置为不同层级,每段动作美感和复杂程度提升, 但是能在每个层级内挑选一个动作, 达到随机衔接招式的目的","layout":null,"expandState":"expand","color":"#d9d9d9","background":"transparent","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di2cbn6tj200","created":1777130887587,"text":"当敌人无法反抗时的斩击动作, (比如眩晕):按住常规x 攻击键的同时摇动手柄摇杆或者鼠标, 驱动动画疯狂斩击敌人","layout":null,"expandState":"expand","color":"#d9d9d9","background":"transparent","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di2chm9yp880","created":1777131355785,"text":"技能树","layout":null,"expandState":"expand","background":"#4a442a","color":"#000000","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2chqybkrk0","created":1777131365965,"text":"让玩家在初始状态就拥有全部技能的使用权力, 但是随着玩家的偏好(例如使用某种技能最多), 那些技能会逐渐变强, 类似于通过训练逐渐掌握技能一样","layout":null,"expandState":"expand","color":"#d9d9d9","background":"transparent","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"digqfznjf4o0","created":1778592563108,"text":"战斗交互机制","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"digqggect4w0","created":1778592599558,"text":"敌人","background":"#a6a6a6","color":"#000000","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"digqgny7xnc0","created":1778592615996,"text":"德库食人草: 根据花瓣开启的方向攻击才能产生伤害","background":"transparent","color":"#d9d9d9","font-weight":"bold","font-family":"arial,helvetica,sans-serif"},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"classic","version":"1.4.43"}